{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "0ec32a56-3cec-407b-8c56-7cb35b23177a", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0ec32a56-3cec-407b-8c56-7cb35b23177a@3.pkg/1772602039413/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602039856", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0ec32a56-3cec-407b-8c56-7cb35b23177a@3.pkg/1772602039413/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602039856"}, "identifier": "0ec32a56-3cec-407b-8c56-7cb35b23177a", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>弓如霹雳弦惊运用比喻的修辞，侧面衬托词人的意气风发、英勇无畏</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读下面两首词，下列题目。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>甲 破阵子&bull;为陈同甫赋壮词以寄之</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>辛弃疾</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>醉里挑灯看剑，梦回吹角连营，八百里分麾下炙，五十弦翻塞外声，沙场秋点兵。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>马作的卢飞快，弓如霹雳弦惊。了却君王天下事，赢得生前身后名，可怜白发生！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>乙 破阵子&bull;四十年来家国 &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>李煜</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>四十年来家国，三千里地山河。凤阁龙楼①连宵汉，玉树球枝作烟萝，几曾识干戈？</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>一旦归为臣虏，沈腰潘鬓②消磨，最是仓皇辞庙③日，教坊犹秦别离歌，垂泪对宫娥。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【注释】①风阁龙楼：指古代帝王居所。②沈腰潘鬓：沈指南朝诗人沈约，后用沈腰指代人日渐消瘦，潘指西晋诗人潘安，后以潘鬓指代中年白发。③庙：亲庙，古代帝王供奉祖先牌位的地方。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>对两首词理解和分析不恰当的一项是（</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">　　</span><span>）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "阅读下面两首词，下列题目。甲 破阵子•为陈同甫赋壮词以寄之辛弃疾醉里挑灯看剑，梦回吹角连营，八百里分麾下炙，五十弦翻塞外声，沙场秋点兵。马作的卢飞快，弓如霹雳弦惊。了却君王天下事，赢得生前身后名，可怜白发生！乙 破阵子•四十年来家国  李煜四十年来家国，三千里地山河。凤阁龙楼①连宵汉，玉树球枝作烟萝，几曾识干戈？一旦归为臣虏，沈腰潘鬓②消磨，最是仓皇辞庙③日，教坊犹秦别离歌，垂泪对宫娥。【注释】①", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0ec32a56-3cec-407b-8c56-7cb35b23177a@3.pkg/item.json?v=1752733252825", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>甲词上片描述军旅生活，醉里点明是酒醉之中，秋点明季节。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>弓如霹雳弦惊运用比喻的修辞，正面衬托词人的意气风发、英勇无畏。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>甲词“可怜白发生！”一句使整首词的风格由变雄壮为悲壮。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>乙词的上片写的是南唐曾有的繁华，下片写的是国破，今昔形成对比。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读下面两首词，下列题目。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>甲 破阵子&bull;为陈同甫赋壮词以寄之</s